      <div xml:id="Aink10-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink10">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
<l>          māri vāykka vaḷanaṉi ciṟakka</l>
<l>          veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
<l>          pūtta māattup pulālañ ciṟumīṉ</l>
<l>          ṟaṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟaṉṉoṭu	</l>
<l>          koṇṭaṉaṉ celka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          'May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
<l>          May the showers be excellent, may fertility be extraordinary,'</l>
<l>          thus wants our mother. We,</l>
<l>          'The man from the village by the cool ghat</l>
<l>          with flowering mango trees [and] reeking little fish:</l>
<l>          let him go as one who takes [us] with him,' thus we want. </l>
          


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
